@startuml 06-finish-maintenance-job
actor "Garage Employee" as Employee
participant WebApp
participant "Workshop Mgmt API" as API
database "Event Store\n(SQL Server)" as ES
queue "RabbitMQ" as MQ

Employee -> WebApp : Mark job as finished
WebApp -> API : FinishMaintenanceJob (HTTP POST)

API -> ES : Load events for WorkshopPlanning aggregate
ES --> API : Event list

note over API : Replay events to\nreconstruct aggregate state

API -> API : Execute command on aggregate
note over API : Produces MaintenanceJobFinished event

API -> ES : Store new events
ES --> API : OK
API -> MQ : Publish MaintenanceJobFinished
API --> WebApp : 200 OK
WebApp --> Employee : Updated planning page

note over MQ : Consumed by Notification Service,\nInvoice Service, Event Handler,\nand Auditlog Service
@enduml
